title: DDFP 605: Week 5 recap & Are the Eagles SB LII contenders?
itunes:title: DDFP 605: Week 5 recap & Are the Eagles SB LII contenders?
description:
Dave Dameshek is joined by Ike Taylor and Dallas Cowboys WR Brice Butler to discuss the Cowboys’ loss to the Packers and whether they left too much time on the clock for Aaron Rodgers. Ike also weighs in on Big Ben’s postgame comments and if he believes Roethlisberger will turn things around. Then, Colleen Wolfe and John Gonzalez join the show to discuss the Eagles’ success this season, and if it’s too soon for the Giants to consider a rebuild. Plus, John and Colleen reenact the first time they met with the help of an EmmaVP screenplay.
